{"Sid":0,"Did":118405,"Id":"282932","Title":"吉祥禪寺","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/da1644cb-4c11-4813-a79d-a0fbab952361/collection/13acee59-4507-484e-ada8-a62a311c0d01/108-sea-pa-1788-201910281828245db6a44c40a4e0.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Place","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n吉祥禪寺位於頭城鎮福成里九股山，又俗稱九股廟，主祀釋迦牟尼佛，是宜蘭縣境內最古老的佛寺。1899年（明治32年）首位住持釋傳豐尋此好山秀水之處開山佈道。 吉祥禪寺位居山腰之上，環境清幽古樸卻不失莊嚴，門聯有約：「吉獻瓊漿法雨濟民歸覺路，祥施甘露航渡世出迷津」。在《蘭陽百景》一書中關於昔日的「新蘭陽八景」之一的吉祥梵宮有如下描述：「九股山中草木深，誰知古寺隱松蔭。叢林鳥雀通禪意，滄海魚龍聽梵音。雙塔凌虛雲欲散，孤燈弄影日將沈。我來不見三生石，空向菩提證素心。」\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.8101989","Keyword_Latitude":"24.8722498","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/place/08FA3A75-5ACB-4421-AF3F-886F275B6EC4","Original_Identifier":"282932","Keyword_Subject_1":"民俗與宗教","alias":"","Keywords":"民間信仰 / 宗教場所 / 廟宇","historicalDates":"","LastUpdateTime":"2020/02/24 00:44:47","timelines":"","place":"","address":"宜蘭縣頭城鎮福成里福德路28號","longitude":"121.8101989","latitude":"24.8722498","phone":"","Event":"","relationPeople":"","open":"0","free":"否","openTime":"","openTimeDescription":"","capacity":"","traffic":"","subjection":"","tag":"","situation":"","historicalDataBrief":"","historicalData":"","reference":"","writer":"莊文生;鄭文嵐;高璇","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","source":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/da1644cb-4c11-4813-a79d-a0fbab952361/collectionOpen/9c41be4c-468a-45e1-b1ff-4244a201b591/108-sea-pa-1788-re-201910281830355db6a44c40a4e0.jpg"}}